{"tid":2498400,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張栢芝為賺人仔突宣佈改名張百知 麥玲玲：名氣不及原名好","createTime":"2021-04-21T06:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T06:45:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"958c89943726dcfd4e1d293a8b60e83d126d83ad","tid":2498400,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"40歲的張栢芝早前參加大陸真人騷《乘風破浪的姐姐2》而增加人氣，可是日前成團之夜，她大熱倒灶不入7 強，未能加入。張栢芝昨日忽然在微博宣佈改新名，她留言：「我的新名字：張百知。」甚至把微博名稱改為「我是張百知」。之後貼出為大陸購物平台拍的宣傳片，扮情報官的她叫自己「張百知」，為賺人仔更索性用新名配合宣傳，不過她的IG就未有改名。<br />\n<br />\n張栢芝這次改名未知是暫時還是永久，其實過往有不少藝人經常改名求轉運。好友張馨予在張栢芝微博八卦提問：「為何突然改名？」網民也加入討論：「我記得張栢芝之前在綜藝說，有人叫她張白癡。」網民也說：「甚麼都知道，所以叫張百知。」有網民樂於叫張百知新名，也有揶揄「改名字好土」，亦有網民擔心：「萬一改不回來怎麼辦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/OR73XP7HYJF6NBFMSJXHU5KOIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FOR73XP7HYJF6NBFMSJXHU5KOIY%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=4f28643d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FOR73XP7HYJF6NBFMSJXHU5KOIY%2F&h=3d235143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/OR73XP7HYJF6NBFMSJXHU5KOIY/</a>"},{"pid":"27224ef001eceb69f31c8b8c0bd8dab104c7a7bf","tid":2498400,"uid":266172,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"張白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f10a437a382d0fce5ccfcdcccaa728f6171e9af","tid":2498400,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"不如叫「張白痴」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffee1b277f3e4348b7fdaa0cc7bbee1f54d654d2","tid":2498400,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"958c89943726dcfd4e1d293a8b60e83d126d83ad","tid":2498400,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021